. * ============================================

. 
. * Table 5: Zero/negative revenue counts (OM undefined)

. 
. * Definition:

. 
. *   - Revenue = total operating revenue (Y1Rev..Y5Rev = driftsinnt aligned by cohort)

. 
. *   - "Zero revenue" INCLUDES missing revenue: (YtRev == 0 OR missing(YtRev))

. 
. *   - Negative revenue: (YtRev < 0) 

. 
. *

. 
. * Special final row (2019 cohort, Year 5=2024, incl. financials):

. 
. *   - Revenue base for pretax margin = driftsinnt2024 + finansinnt2024

. 
. *   - "Zero pretax revenue" includes missing: (revbase == 0 OR missing(revbase))

. 
. * ============================================

. 
. 
. 
. display as text "Period                              Zero revenue (n)    Negative revenue (n)"
Period                              Zero revenue (n)    Negative revenue (n)

. 
. display as text "--------------------------------------------------------------------------"
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

. 
. 
. 
. * ---- Year 1 to Year 5 (relative year after registration) ----

. 
. forvalues t = 1/5 {
  2. 
.     quietly count if (Y`t'Rev == 0 | missing(Y`t'Rev))
  3. 
.     local z = r(N)
  4. 
.     quietly count if (Y`t'Rev < 0)
  5. 
.     local n = r(N)
  6. 
. 
. 
.     display as result "Year `t' " %34s "" %10.0f `z' "              " %10.0f `n'
  7. 
. }
Year 1                                        26719                      64
Year 2                                        28020                      97
Year 3                                        29922                     107
Year 4                                        31958                     127
Year 5                                        33780                     111

. 
. * ---- Aggregated Year 1-5 (rowtotal treats missing as 0, which is desired) ----

. 
. tempvar Rev_agg_1to5

. 
. egen double `Rev_agg_1to5' = rowtotal(Y1Rev Y2Rev Y3Rev Y4Rev Y5Rev)

. 
. quietly count if (`Rev_agg_1to5' == 0 | missing(`Rev_agg_1to5'))

. 
. local agg_zero = r(N)

. 
. quietly count if (`Rev_agg_1to5' < 0)

. 
. local agg_neg = r(N)

. 
. display as result "Year 1-5 aggregated " %20s "" %10.0f `agg_zero' "              " %10.0f `agg_neg'
Year 1-5 aggregated                          21002                      87

. 
. * ---- Special row: Year 5 (2019 cohort only) incl. financial income in revenue base ----

. 
. * Revenue base for pretax margin denominator = driftsinnt2024 + finansinnt2024

. 
. * rowtotal makes missing components count as 0 -> aligns with "missing counts as zero revenue".

. 
. tempvar RevBase_Y5_2019

. 
. egen double `RevBase_Y5_2019' = rowtotal(driftsinnt2024 finansinnt2024) if RegYear == 2019
(29,904 missing values generated)

. 
. quietly count if RegYear == 2019 & (`RevBase_Y5_2019' == 0 | missing(`RevBase_Y5_2019'))

. 
. local y5_zero = r(N)

. 
. quietly count if RegYear == 2019 & (`RevBase_Y5_2019' < 0)

. 
. local y5_neg = r(N)

. 
. display as result "Year 5 (2019 cohort, incl. fin. income) " %5s "" %10.0f `y5_zero' "              " %10.0f `y5_neg'
